data.description: Nice & spacious corner lot home offers 4 bedrooms & open floor plan with high ceilings! Living and dining areas. Kitchen comes with all stainless steel appliances and island. Spacious zoned primary bedroom with walk in closet. Primary bath with dual sinks and jetted tub. Ceramic tile in main areas, carpet in bedrooms only. Laundry area in main hallway that includes washer and dryer. Good size yard with pergola. 2 car detached garage with opener. Close to schools, parks, shopping and entertainment. Come and make this house your home!
